data.title: What is it like to live in Östersund, Sweden?
data.meta_description:
Answer: That’s my town. Östersund is an old garrison town with about 50.000 inhabitants. It is situated by a large lake that looks smaller than it is because of the island of Frösö, which obscures the vast expanses of Lake Storsjön from the town centre.
